# Windows Configuration Profile

## Purpose

Standardize company devices.

## Settings

- Disable Guest Account
- Enable BitLocker
- Enable Firewall
- Configure Windows Update
- Disable USB Storage (Example)
- Configure Microsoft Defender

## Result

All enrolled devices receive identical security settings automatically.
