troubleshooting/common-issues.md
# Common Intune Issues

## Device Not Appearing

Possible Causes

- Enrollment failure
- User licensing issue
- Internet connectivity
- Sync delay

## Policies Not Applying

Check

- Device Sync
- User Assignment
- Group Membership
- Compliance Status

## Company Portal Problems

- Verify login
- Update Company Portal
- Restart device
- Sync manually

## Device Shows Non-Compliant

Possible Reasons

- Encryption disabled
- Antivirus disabled
- Outdated OS
